_sText: Well after working on this awhile and Releasing pictures to the Waspnest community, I'm done. There are four stories you can go on all of the rooms can be breached by the zombies. The doors aren't effected by the object, because if they were then the cts would always win :). I have also placed a USEFUL camera in the security room. It will tell you if those pesky zombies are outside the room out of our sight.
